column8:
继@3之后，@1也倒下了。@1的左胸口开始溢出黑色的黏液。他们不肯相信我，他们都看不到，可是那里真的有黑色的黏液，像泥浆一样滴落下来……

@3总是笑着说是他遗传了这种无名怪病给@1，所以他俩才相继病倒。我握着他苍白的手，看着他日益衰弱的模样和肩头越来越大的黑色创口，不知道该如何是好。

……他们骗人，写下来对我没有任何帮助。

column9:
After @3 collapsed, @1 followed suit. Black ooze began seeping from @1's left chest. They refused to believe me; they couldn't see it, but black ooze was indeed dripping down like sludge...

@3 always joked that he had passed this nameless disease to @1, which explained their consecutive illnesses. I held his pale hand, watching his weakening condition and the growing black wound on his shoulder, unsure of what to do.

...They lie. Writing it down doesn't help me at all.

column8:
5月3日
@1去世了。
@3没有来参加她的葬礼，因为他已经虚弱得无法离开病床。
